{"tid":2195402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"103萬樣本僅18確診 林鄭認比率低","createTime":"2020-09-09T07:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T03:46:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":93,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff507de5f2840a2dc4b2c212efdff4557b455d6","tid":2195402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/ZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=741db62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I%2F&h=60a46bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/ZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n103萬樣本僅18確診 林鄭認比率低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FagHCG8wV5o9c61kWpCrhGieLOA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6W2QITHA2ZDTTCWFEXGFRNTQJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFagHCG8wV5o9c61kWpCrhGieLOA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6W2QITHA2ZDTTCWFEXGFRNTQJY.jpg&h=836af3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■全民檢測推行已一星期，林鄭鼓勵未預約市民即場排隊參加。 中新社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全民檢測推行一星期，累計已化驗逾100萬個樣本，但至昨日只驗出18人確診，比率為0 .0017%。曾聲稱社區有1,500個隱形患者的特首林鄭月娥昨承認，確診比例非常低，但當局仍會考慮延長計劃，並鼓勵市民毋須預約，直接到各檢測中心即場檢測。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港研開關 旅遊氣泡無台灣  與11國商討 日本泰國最積極<br />\n<br />\n政府昨晚公佈，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仍稱視情況是否再延長<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨在行政會議前承認，全民檢測至今找到的確診個案比例非常低，但認為仍有助全面了解本港目前感染情況。她又表示，無預約下到場檢測的人數由初期的18%上升至26%，尚餘數天的檢測計劃中已預留更多名額讓市民即場登記檢測，歡迎市民在毋須登記下參加檢測。當局會視乎情況決定是否再延長，計劃最長會進行 14 天。<br />\n<br />\n至於全民檢測出現首宗「假陽性」個案，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bd2dae79cc86e1f249aaf40f9209b450eb1dc157","tid":2195402,"uid":36383,"like":95,"dislike":3,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"False negative 呢？"},{"pid":"1b8c44a74eaebc45296102ba75d94de4c172d92c","tid":2195402,"uid":173425,"like":166,"dislike":3,"score":163,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"參與人數1m, 即係得番呢班人信個政府<br />\n<br />\n利申:深藍老細開始叫同事去驗，有部分深藍同事已做，手足同事不為所動"},{"pid":"9223f39fce558be38495cb9849a4f7720e85a40e","tid":2195402,"uid":179775,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:19:40.000Z","msg":"18個有幾多過係中過再去驗"},{"pid":"8bd2fb15083d55d8819ef577578f78d45d35e5e6","tid":2195402,"uid":2645,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"103萬有幾多係重刷？"},{"pid":"647981020b54750112e82eb5679e5ba93e40dd10","tid":2195402,"uid":16676,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"唔封關害死多100條人命唔使負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781143fed578ef142bf9a34d2eec35ceaf9cfc26","tid":2195402,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"當初林鄭話有中央支持可以日驗50萬，點知驗成個星期先驗得100萬個<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2195419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2195419</a>"},{"pid":"5ccfa74d973e65c7296c07f4a068e003016a5e6c","tid":2195402,"uid":41116,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"講錯鳩鳩無成本<br />\nwhy not"},{"pid":"111e4691b4e30c1188d49c61a24b42dfaf93639f","tid":2195402,"uid":10014,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"其實真係有100萬？"},{"pid":"30f8dd05aa411678dcb9fae43eda7be7a361d7ba","tid":2195402,"uid":45353,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"111e4691b4e30c1188d49c61a24b42dfaf93639f","tid":2195402,"uid":10014,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"其實真係有100萬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2