r />\n我vlookup搵唔到佢哋係同一個人喎，吹咩"},{"pid":"98085ce1ee0dd865c2d394be3d611717d641e122","tid":2195402,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d8ee558ccb7eb17a90d45125f406769ce19cfa","tid":2195402,"uid":229479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:27:14.000Z","msg":"林鄭思維：姐係600萬人反政府反中共？"},{"pid":"d04e292e30217101c2e2c6661fbfb6c1e7cdb3c6","tid":2195402,"uid":277282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ff507de5f2840a2dc4b2c212efdff4557b455d6","tid":2195402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/ZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=741db62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I%2F&h=60a46bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/ZNOJAWXVPRBC7FEM3KINPGXQ5I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n103萬樣本僅18確診 林鄭認比率低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FagHCG8wV5o9c61kWpCrhGieLOA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6W2QITHA2ZDTTCWFEXGFRNTQJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFagHCG8wV5o9c61kWpCrhGieLOA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6W2QITHA2ZDTTCWFEXGFRNTQJY.jpg&h=836af3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■全民檢測推行已一星期，林鄭鼓勵未預約市民即場排隊參加。 中新社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全民檢測推行一星期，累計已化驗逾100萬個樣本，但至昨日只驗出18人確診，比率為0 .0017%。曾聲稱社區有1,500個隱形患者的特首林鄭月娥昨承認，確診比例非常低，但當局仍會考慮延長計劃，並鼓勵市民毋須預約，直接到各檢測中心即場檢測。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港研開關 旅遊氣泡無台灣  與11國商討 日本泰國最積極<br />\n<br />\n政府昨晚公佈，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仍稱視情況是否再延長<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨在行政會議前承認，全民檢測至今找到的確診個案比例非常低，但認為仍有助全面了解本港目前感染情況。她又表示，無預約下到場檢測的人數由初期的18%上升至26%，尚餘數天的檢測計劃中已預留更多名額讓市民即場登記檢測，歡迎市民在毋須登記下參加檢測。當局會視乎情況決定是否再延長，計劃最長會進行 14 天。<br />\n<br />\n至於全民檢測出現首宗「假陽性」個案，。。。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:33:14.000Z","msg":"我估採樣員亂鳩嚟"},{"pid":"697d6f08552dd5f1485ae9f52fb7932003d89523","tid":2195402,"uid":17399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:35:00.000Z","msg":"全民檢測 (100萬人) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c61f9153b6202abda2ee05c689d2b892e43d72a","tid":2195402,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:39:47.000Z","msg":"仲要已經康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多鳩餘"},{"pid":"7b890302d38e0e1cd4c6359d4f12229b98524c82","tid":2195402,"uid":288393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b8c44a74eaebc45296102ba75d94de4c172d92c","tid":2195402,"uid":173425,"like":166,"dislike":3,"score":163,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"參與人數1m, 即係得番呢班人信個政府<br />\n<br />\n利申:深藍老細開始叫同事去驗，有部分深藍同事已做，手足同事不為所動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:42:52.000Z","msg":"開始聽到啲唔驗即自撚私論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42d83f6e38cef2de3304fab65bf13e988b00e0a","tid":2195402,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"淋病：「錢已送中， 吹鳩我漲」"},{"pid":"1ec19f5fdf2ad1767e9fc5b0842af72010db297f","tid":2195402,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c77fe746ae7daff9427481f00b633759005b658","tid":2195402,"uid":75196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"確診人數少，咁唔係好事黎咩"},{"pid":"4b1e50e46b25875ef696f486dbd52d86f09e99eb","tid":2195402,"uid":223084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc